{
  "id": "69c9eddc943e989705dd6c2c",
  "title": "自分の体調不良を感じる瞬間",
  "created": 1774841315,
  "updated": 1774842880,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c9eddc943e989705dd6c2c",
      "text": "自分の体調不良を感じる瞬間",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841315,
      "updated": 1774841315
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9ede30000000000f12370",
      "text": "\t音がやたらと耳に響く時[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841315,
      "updated": 1774841327
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9eded0000000000f12372",
      "text": "\t\t多分[水分不足]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841325,
      "updated": 1774841343
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9ee0d0000000000f12375",
      "text": "\t\t姿勢変えるとごわわって感じがする",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841356,
      "updated": 1774841368
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9eded0000000000f12371",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841325,
      "updated": 1774841325
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9edf10000000000f12373",
      "text": "仕事してると常時体調不良なのでよくわかんない[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841328,
      "updated": 1774841338
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9edf80000000000f12374",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841335,
      "updated": 1774841335
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9eea20000000000c6a623",
      "text": "散歩の時に、嫌な考えが脳みそぐるぐるしてる時[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1774841506,
      "updated": 1774841571
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9eeee0000000000c6a625",
      "text": " 「あ、こりゃいかん。とっととやってるのを片付けて一回寝るべ」となるアラート",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1774841582,
      "updated": 1774841629
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9eeca0000000000c6a624",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1774841545,
      "updated": 1774841545
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9f3ff00000000003f5f0f",
      "text": "\t[体調が悪いと不機嫌になる]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
